skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: hour music umair
des:
You will be playing with Alexa, the DJ in this skill. Alexa will pick a random song for you and will sing some lyrics from that song. Have fun singing along with DJ Alexa! 
Note: There is no autotune or beats in the background of the song. Alexa will sing a plain song, nothing too special.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
